comments: Jokic (DEN) is drawn into the air on the pump fake and is not in a legal guarding position as he makes contact with Nurkic (PHX) during his shot attempt near the basket.
Durant (PHX) delivers body contact to Jokic (DEN) and affects Jokic's SQBR during the drive.
Durant (PHX) reaches in defending Jokic (DEN) and makes contact with the ball, causing it to become loose.
Jackson (DEN) briefly places his hands on Durant (PHX) on the perimeter and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Nurkic (PHX) extends his elbow into Jokic's (DEN) face/head.  All flagrant fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Okogie (PHX) leans into Caldwell-Pope (DEN) defending him on the perimeter but the contact is marginal.
Okogie (PHX) grazes the inside of Jokic's (DEN) left arm and the contact does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) briefly brings his arms around Durant (PHX), who pulls his arms away to release from the contact and receive the throw-in.
Durant (PHX) reaches across Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) body and the contact is marginal.
Allen (PHX) gets his hand on the ball, but initiates more than marginal contact with Porter Jr.'s (DEN) arm.
